{"tid":1606582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[FC] 190930 星島A7 一群愛護香港的專業人士的聲明","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T14:49:35.000Z","uid":46487,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"51d5570f77c659874464fc537ac227732faca3e0","tid":1606582,"uid":46487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7KkNzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7KkNzM.jpg&h=9660e2ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今日星島A7 刊出左將近<span style=\"color: red;\">一千個</span>來自建造工程界專業人士嘅簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信係應對返我地話有好多專業人士係黃<br />\n鑑於小弟太無聊 所以上左 Architects Registration Board 個網進行cross check:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.arb.org.hk/TheRegister.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.arb.org.hk%2FTheRegister.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=73516091\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.arb.org.hk/TheRegister.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港現時有 3839 個註冊建築師<br />\n聯署入名有 320 個自稱建築師嘅簽名<br />\n比對結果如下<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/NEHJCxu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FNEHJCxu&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b514ecd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/NEHJCxu</a><br />\n有160 個簽名成功比對到<br />\n155 個比對唔到 大約10個重覆嘅簽名<br />\n<br />\n以下係簽名指向單一結果嘅建築師名單 有104個<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">區浩章   歐陽麗絲   陳澤斌   陳萬光   陳俊傑   陳慧芳   陳逸俊   陳玄昭   陳耀輝   \n周冠棠   鄭仲良   鄭振揚   鄭東   張文政   錢永德   趙智成   周炯道   周嘉穎   \n周子芳   鄒慧玲   朱寶林   朱藹欣   朱若思   鍾詠琪   符展成   馮紫珊   馮漢聰   \n夏士鴻   何靜荷   何頌豪   何仲怡   何承澤   何淑珍   何永豪   何宇軒   許文博   \n洪志波   簡志為   龔啟源   關秉渲   鄺永強   黎嘉敏   黎珮汶   黎紹堅   黎詠儀   \n林材發   林鳳權   林癸生   林穎璋   林煒彬   羅維昇   李仲明   李焯華   李明偉   \n李洵鈺   梁志佳   梁志強   梁文傑   梁百勤   李震鑾   李可堅   李燕群   林雲峰   \n連漢文   廖永康   盧建能   馬志剛   馬濤   馬永華   文連有   吳克正   吳玠廸   \n吳芷瑩   彭浩賢   彭國樑   彭美端   沈維立   單子浩   薛志威   蕭陞揚   邵德明   \n宋浩綸   譚天放   鄧啟聰   鄧文傑   鄧譚娜妮   鄧育恒   鄧耀鈞   杜曉明   謝正勤   \n徐靖生   徐逸鏗   衞翠芷   溫嘉儀   黃兆鈞   黃偉鵬   黃婉儀   胡俊豪   邱文衛   \n楊俊傑   楊振光   楊鑑賢   葉思進   余家聲   </code></pre><br />\n以下係比對不成功嘅名單, 155 個<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">HY JOHN YIU    KS JENNIFER TANG    T IP    WL YIU    TY LI    MP CHU    LK MA    LC MA    YW AU    WC TANG    HC LEE    LP CHU    WT AU    CK SHUM    KC AU    KI YIP    YE WONG    MC KAN    CB HUI    CP CHU    MC LEE    FN CHU    CP LEE    S MAN    HT TUNG    FH LAM    WH CHAU    KY WUN    KC CHAU    TL CHAT    MA WANG    YM CHING    MT CHIU    YP TANG    MW SUEN    WO TSUI    HW SUEN    SH LAM    KC SUEN    TM CHU    HC TUNG    KW TSUI    YO TUNG    LK CHU    KH SY    HA AU    LH LAW    SS KUNG    KE NGAN    YE SHUM    WP KWAN    MS KWAN    PT KAM    YD HONG    SN KAM    HB ANG    CE LEE    SE NG    DK MOK    CN HO    YH HSU    WJ MOK    YS SHUM    NN CHOW    LC WONG    TF WONG    KG LEE    BK NG    CL LUN    HD CHAN    MY MOK    MP KWAN    YK LIN    MT SIU    CP SHUI    MC CHAN    FC CHAN    TK LEUNG    FS CHEUNG    KA NG    WK LI    PC CHOW    WS PANG    MW DAI    GY LUK    HC LUK    SW LUI    CK LUN    YL CHUNG    LK LEE    YW LEE    LK WONG    KF WU    HN SIT    YY TANG    MT PAK    LW LUK    YK NG KA    ZOE SONG    WY YUEN    DYN WONG    LS LAM    SH LAM    HN LAM    KK WANG    KT TSUI    SC TSUI    WK NG    WS NAM    KT MOK    CH TSE    LY LAI    FK WONG    MK WONG    KE WONG    NK LAM    LK LAM    CM CHUNG    KS CHUNG    KY SZE    MK SY    FW SUNG    KH CHO    WS WAN    KT CHING    FC CHO    CH TSE    MW CHAO    WC TSE    DENISE WU    EDDIE LEE    OS WONG    MK JOSEPH TAM    YK CHAU    MH CHAU    LK TSE    SH CHUM    ERIC WK CHUM    JOHN T. SZETO    YJ CHENG    CP CHEUNG    EDMOND FY MOK    CW CHO    PETER    K. MAK    H. CHAN    B. WONG    D. TANG    J. LEE    J. LAU    </code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結論: 類推呢一千個名有起碼一半係9作出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後上面名單嘅人士都未必真係佢地有份簽名<br />\n因為好容易撞中, 例子: 3800 人名單入面有8 個SL CHAN</span><br />\n<br />\n最後 根據 《建築師註冊條例》<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不是名列註冊紀錄冊內的人不得自稱為&ldquo;建築師&rdquo;</span>或&ldquo;註冊建築師&rdquo;，或在姓名後加上英文縮寫&ldquo;R.A.&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌我係咪認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95442bd9b93d52b63a32371e859d6f792400113f","tid":1606582,"uid":46487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55c9eac5b5691c3c4a686fd9f61d267881e2964","tid":1606582,"uid":79903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"b0542b97edefcad799ad47dc33e231ae88a6cbd8","tid":1606582,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"造假不意外"},{"pid":"236bf62c312f80bb9f880941d62956c0a830b14d","tid":1606582,"uid":46487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0542b97edefcad799ad47dc33e231ae88a6cbd8","tid":1606582,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"造假不意外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"不意外都要求證<br />\n同埋我相信有真心簽名嘅人<br />\n所以立此為証遲啲清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1e1450c2b225dde609273b2882a80cf2764af3","tid":1606582,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"假架，好多人俾人冒認"},{"pid":"4b557bfb9f6f34a6f37e4e53f4a9acf7171ddba9","tid":1606582,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df1afb6dc26b597d8a7d3320d157413bdb7bbc27","tid":1606582,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0542b97edefcad799ad47d